## What you need to modify

Your project has 9 files. You only need to care about 3:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `src/app/page.tsx` | Home page | **Every time** |
| `src/app/` (your routes) | App Router pages and API routes | **Every time** |
| `tests/` | Tests for components and routes | **Every time** |
| Others (next.config.ts, ESLint) | Project infra | Almost never |

## Quick Start

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start development server (Turbopack) |
| `npm run build` | Build for production |
| `npm start` | Run production build |
| `npm test` | Run tests once (Vitest) |
| `npm run test:watch` | Run tests in watch mode |
| `npm run lint` | Lint with ESLint |

